    <item>
      <title>成本和镇压阻碍了巴基斯坦的竞选活动</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/costs-crackdown-put-damper-pakistans-election-campaigns-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[较高的生活成本和政治不确定性使巴基斯坦一度热闹的竞选活动变得平淡，候选人和为他们提供材料的人都哀叹需要用更少的钱做更多的事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/costs-crackdown-put-damper-pakistans-election-campaigns-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 02:24:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路透调查显示印尼第四季度经济可能增长5%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesias-economy-likely-have-grown-5-q4-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社对 23 名经济学家进行的调查发现，尽管出口萎缩且大宗商品价格下跌，但在国内消费强劲的支撑下，印度尼西亚第四季度经济同比增长 5.0%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesias-economy-likely-have-grown-5-q4-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 01:54:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲思考美联储的影响，债券仍看好降息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街股市尾盘暴跌后，亚洲股市周四下跌，而投资者仍押注美国今年将大幅降息，即使现在开始降息的时间可能比最初希望的要晚一些。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 01:50:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国国防部长前往中东举行会谈和军火博览会</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/skorea-defence-minister-heads-middle-east-talks-arms-expo-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国国防部称，韩国国防部长申元植将于周四启程前往中东进行为期 7 天的访问，举行部长级会谈并参加在沙特阿拉伯举行的武器展览。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/skorea-defence-minister-heads-middle-east-talks-arms-expo-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 01:36:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国工厂活动 19 个月来首次扩张 - PMI</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-factory-activity-expands-first-time-19-months-pmi-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四的一项私营部门调查显示，随着主要出口市场需求改善，产量和订单恢复增长，韩国 1 月份工厂活动出现 19 个月来的首次扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-factory-activity-expands-first-time-19-months-pmi-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 01:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度莫迪可能在大选前预算中提出温和的经济宣言</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-likely-lay-out-modest-economic-manifesto-pre-election-budget-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪政府将于周四在选举前公布最终预算，预计该计划将在财政上采取审慎态度，重点关注基础设施支出，但在全国投票前传递大量政治信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-likely-lay-out-modest-economic-manifesto-pre-election-budget-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 00:32:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芯片销量激增、中国反弹，韩国出口连续第四个月增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-jan-exports-rise-fourth-month-chip-sales-surge-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国 1 月份出口连续第四个月增长，原因是对中国的销售反弹以及六年来最大的芯片出货量激增，在 2024 年初提振了依赖贸易的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-jan-exports-rise-fourth-month-chip-sales-surge-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 00:25:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡吉宝船舶销售年利润翻两番</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/singapores-keppel-annual-profit-more-than-quadruples-2024-01-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡吉宝周四公布，其全年利润增长了四倍多，这主要得益于剥离其离岸和海事 (O&amp;M) 部门的一次性收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/singapores-keppel-annual-profit-more-than-quadruples-2024-01-31/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 23:43:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡交易所高收益利润大幅增长，近期全球增长黯淡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/singapore-exchanges-half-yearly-profit-rises-6-2024-01-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡交易所（SGX）周四公布半年度利润大幅增长，受到货币和大宗商品衍生品业务的支撑，但也指出地缘政治紧张局势加剧和宏观环境充满挑战带来的阻力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/singapore-exchanges-half-yearly-profit-rises-6-2024-01-31/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 22:52:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能推动下，高通利润预测超出预期，股价波动</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-forecasts-quarterly-profit-above-estimates-2024-01-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高通周三预测第二财季利润略高于华尔街预期，销售额符合市场预期，但投资者对该芯片制造商的Android在中国的销售感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-forecasts-quarterly-profit-above-estimates-2024-01-31/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 21:00:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
